      "span_text": "The main function of fatty acid synthase is to catalyze the synthesis of palmitate from acetyl-CoA and malonyl-CoA. Elongation of long chain fatty acids 6 (ELOVL6) is an elongase that catalyzes the conversion of palmitate to stearate  ."
